Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.11,0:00:45.55,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,欢迎来到7G网络启动仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.55,0:00:49.17,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,您正是第七万七千七百七十七位顾客
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.17,0:00:50.07,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,请问该怎么称呼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.07,0:00:50.91,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.91,0:00:52.23,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.88,0:00:55.58,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,我叫中富叶香
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.58,0:00:57.45,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,叶香小姐 欢迎欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.45,0:01:02.02,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,我是全球7G委员会会长 波伊森·毒太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.45,0:01:02.02,annotation,Sign,0,0,0,,即Poison Pontaro
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.02,0:01:05.21,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,叶香小姐对史上最快链接全世界的7G网络
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.21,0:01:07.22,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,有什么期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.67,0:01:10.57,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,期待？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.57,0:01:11.62,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.62,0:01:14.24,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,无论何地 无论何人 全部链接 Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.24,0:01:16.80,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,这就是梦想中的新技术 7G
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.80,0:01:18.69,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,我们没赶上5G的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.69,0:01:20.64,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,6G又参与得太晚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.64,0:01:23.51,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,但是 7G终于夺回了这个国家的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.51,0:01:25.98,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,虽然还是有那么些人反对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.98,0:01:27.14,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,还有黑子指指点点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.14,0:01:30.73,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,但是面对他们那些fake news 我们绝不退缩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.73,0:01:34.90,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,世界最前沿的技术 全在7G 只在7G
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.90,0:01:38.01,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,采用全方位装置 直接读取大脑念头
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.01,0:01:40.62,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,思想即刻传递 念头瞬间成真
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.62,0:01:43.69,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,正可谓是神明的力量 这就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.69,0:01:45.31,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,7G
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.32,0:01:46.62,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,{\an8}欸 我能离开了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.58,0:01:48.98,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,那么接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.98,0:01:50.90,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,就请大家一同见证
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.90,0:01:52.68,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,通向未来的历史性一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.25,0:01:54.27,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,五
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.79,0:01:55.58,Default,Group,0,0,0,,四
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.12,0:01:57.09,Default,Group,0,0,0,,三
