Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.45,0:13:23.94,annotation,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs12\frz9.416\pos(905.2,662.8)}各地警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.45,0:13:23.94,annotation,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs20\frz10.43\pos(892.4,562.8)}紧急招募第四次\N新宿涩谷探险队队员
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.88,0:13:24.56,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,别那么在意嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.42,0:13:26.95,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,怎么了 静留
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.20,0:13:29.75,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,竟然还有新报纸在出版啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.75,0:13:32.29,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,「列车运行图大门逐渐增大」上面这样写着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.75,0:13:32.29,annotation,Sign,0,0,0,,列车运行图大门 Diagram Gate\N是开头叶香他们启动7G时所在大楼的名字\N这楼是西武集团给自己盖的办公大楼\N整体寓意是列车穿过大楼就像穿过一座运行图竖起的大门
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:33.21,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,这啥意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.21,0:13:34.80,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,这个 难道说就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.80,0:13:35.87,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,什么什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.87,0:13:36.98,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,叶香！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.98,0:13:38.35,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,哈？怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.35,0:13:40.46,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,叶香！真的是叶香！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.46,0:13:42.09,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,哈？这个叶香是那个叶香吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.09,0:13:44.23,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,还有哪个叫叶香的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.37,0:13:45.45,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,呜哇 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.45,0:13:46.48,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,这是什么时候的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.48,0:13:47.39,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是上个月的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.39,0:13:48.23,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.23,0:13:49.51,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,完全没法相信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.51,0:13:51.95,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,她在池袋做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.95,0:13:54.75,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我要告诉小雪奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.75,0:13:56.20,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.71,0:14:03.02,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,两年前的那天后 世界完全改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.02,0:14:06.56,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,车站之间的距离 城镇之间的距离
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:08.41,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,突然延长到无法跨越
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.64,0:14:09.94,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不仅是距离
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.18,0:14:12.96,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,人和生物全都变了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.36,0:14:17.24,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,在吾野的成年人都变成了动物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.24,0:14:20.93,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,现在虽然还存留有人类的常识
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.93,0:14:25.95,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但感觉总有一天 可能会真的变成动物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.24,0:14:29.73,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不过吾野之外 或许更加严峻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.24,0:14:29.59,annotation,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不同车站受到7G的影响不同\N吾野变成了动物\N至于其他车站的情况，敬请期待
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.12,0:14:31.34,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.34,0:14:32.43,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,小雪奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:33.01,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.84,0:14:50.07,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,最初大家都震惊了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.07,0:14:52.62,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,自己变成了奇怪的动物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:55.40,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,愤怒 自暴自弃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.71,0:15:00.14,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,一些人组成调查小组 冒险前往别处
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.14,0:15:03.26,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,一半的人中途放弃折返回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.26,0:15:05.00,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,剩下的一半再也没有回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.24,0:15:07.68,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,小雪奶奶哭了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.71,0:15:11.01,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,可能是因为 知道自己唯一的孙女还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.11,0:15:12.31,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,很高兴的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.31,0:15:13.53,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.73,0:15:15.94,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,小雪奶奶也没变年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.94,0:15:18.35,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,豚鼠好像只能活五六年吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.35,0:15:18.95,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.95,0:15:21.43,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,为什么小晶你要说这些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.43,0:15:23.16,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,是玲实你先提到她年龄的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.23,0:15:24.96,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,小晶你是真的神经粗大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.03,0:15:26.93,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,明明我是久违地好心教你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.15,0:15:26.93,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,{\an8}好好相处！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:30.55,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.76,0:15:32.93,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,{\an8}抓住你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.64,0:15:41.95,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.92,0:15:49.21,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,异变的原因 听说都是7G网络失控的错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.47,0:15:52.82,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是 完全不知道如何恢复原状
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.02,0:15:55.55,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,或者说 我感觉根本没人想那样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.56,0:15:59.81,Default,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,欢迎回家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.81,0:16:00.87,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.87,0:16:02.55,Default,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,晚饭还有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.55,0:16:04.96,Default,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,虽然还是一如既往的苦瓜饭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.96,0:16:06.34,Default,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,但你要先加热后再吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.34,0:16:07.80,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.10,0:16:13.07,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,该说是托7G的福还是受7G所累 总之电还通着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.88,0:16:18.29,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,虽然没法看电视和上网 但是近距离还能用小灵通
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.65,0:16:23.58,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,冰箱虽然还能用 但是和微波炉同时用就会跳闸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.78,0:16:27.59,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,没法像过去那样随便用了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:30.41,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,说到底这是不是电也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.06,0:16:35.26,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,叫它沿着轨道传播的电类能量才对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.16,0:16:39.92,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.92,0:16:42.03,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,静留你原来是这种人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.61,0:16:43.67,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.79,0:16:45.67,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,「这种人」是什么意思啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.77,0:16:47.66,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,叶香你才是这种人吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.97,0:16:49.33,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.23,0:16:52.24,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,毕竟我就是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.10,0:16:53.93,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.63,0:16:56.16,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你道什么歉啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.33,0:16:59.49,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我不管你了啊！叶香！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.76,0:17:02.48,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,真是的 那家伙什么意思嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.35,0:17:06.28,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那晚之后 我就再也没见过叶香
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.59,0:17:07.68,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我们没碰过面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.82,0:17:09.46,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我也没找到她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.46,0:17:13.84,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这谁找得到嘛 怎么在池袋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.92,0:17:16.16,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我还以为她就在吾野附近呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.20,0:17:18.84,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这两年 我还一直在找
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.84,0:17:20.13,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.50,0:17:21.63,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,波奇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.87,0:17:26.79,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,波奇 你怎么就没变成人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.79,0:17:29.39,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,既然所有人长大后都会变成动物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.45,0:17:31.73,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那波奇你变成人也不奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.17,0:17:33.69,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,确实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.92,0:17:37.65,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,如果叶香就在附近 波奇应该也会告诉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.65,0:17:39.00,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,毕竟她是你的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.68,0:17:42.07,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我怎么从来没注意到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.96,0:17:46.19,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.19,0:17:47.30,Default,Group,0,0,0,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.39,0:17:54.17,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,善治郎先生 你怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.17,0:17:56.30,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,站在这种地方可是很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:17:57.34,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.61,0:18:00.47,Default,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,帽 帽子…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.71,0:18:01.09,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,帽子？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.32,0:18:06.12,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.89,0:18:09.94,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,帽绳…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.94,0:18:11.86,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,波奇 知道这个是什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.05,0:18:15.78,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶 知道的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.78,0:18:16.51,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.51,0:18:18.56,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,善治郎先生 那边很危险的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.54,0:18:31.62,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这里面有什么东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.24,0:18:48.95,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.02,0:18:50.85,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啵啵的帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.18,0:18:53.80,Zenjiro,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,毒太郎那个混账狗屎！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.91,0:18:56.03,Zenjiro,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,我都说了那么多次让他放弃7G了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.12,0:18:57.93,Zenjiro,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,那种企划怎么可能有效
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.97,0:18:58.82,Zenjiro,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶——！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.93,0:19:03.27,Zenjiro,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,对诸多研究者「可能破坏物理法则」的警告充耳不闻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.49,0:19:06.39,Zenjiro,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,盲目接受利益相关者的不可靠情报
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.43,0:19:09.38,Zenjiro,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,犯了一次错还不够 居然还要再错下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.45,0:19:10.94,Zenjiro,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,婊子混账臭废物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:12.30,Zenjiro,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,不仅要妨碍我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.34,0:19:14.45,Zenjiro,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,还用喵喵技术让我喵喵了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.34,0:19:17.00,annotation,Sign,0,0,0,,善次郎一直在表达7G网络的危险性\N因此，他被强制进行了一项神秘的手术作为封口\N“うにゃうにゃ”是某种手术的隐语
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.54,0:19:16.94,Zenjiro,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,实际无可救药 冷酷无情之辈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.19,0:19:18.55,Zenjiro,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,但你等着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.19,0:19:23.02,annotation,Sign,0,0,0,,善次郎在手术后被遗弃在了他的故乡吾野\N之所以他仍然保持着人类的形态\N是因为在进行“うにゃうにゃ”手术之前\N他住在另一个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.59,0:19:20.68,Zenjiro,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,我绝对会把7G停给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.76,0:19:22.87,Zenjiro,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,不会让你霸占池袋据点的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.99,0:19:24.35,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,等等 你说池袋了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.35,0:19:25.16,Zenjiro,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.23,0:19:26.89,Zenjiro,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,池袋可不能继续这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.98,0:19:28.17,Zenjiro,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,不尽快阻止他的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.17,0:19:31.40,Zenjiro,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,事出紧急 我平善治郎只能开动这2000系列车
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.17,0:19:31.40,annotation,Sign,0,0,0,,选择2000系列车作为舞台\N是因为西武线给人的印象就是黄色电车
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.54,0:19:33.20,Zenjiro,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,不对 等等 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.76,0:19:36.76,Zenjiro,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,你是 千仓静留吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:38.42,Zenjiro,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,你小的时候跌到泥沟里…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.42,0:19:39.46,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,怎样都好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.54,0:19:41.86,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,重要的是这个2000什么的要怎么开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.86,0:19:43.66,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你会开车吗 善治郎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.76,0:19:46.19,Default,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,你说我会不会开车？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.38,0:19:47.00,Default,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,那当然…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.74,0:19:51.50,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶—！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.54,0:19:52.11,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不是搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.16,0:19:53.37,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,给我再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.56,0:19:55.95,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这次怎么不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.95,0:19:57.32,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.32,0:19:59.57,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊— 搞什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.22,0:20:03.39,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,什么东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.45,0:20:06.52,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,帽子怎么又不能变了 怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.60,0:20:07.93,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,喂 你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.84,0:20:09.80,Default,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.51,0:20:12.04,Default,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,千万小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.34,0:20:14.14,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,谢谢你 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.44,0:20:15.19,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.68,0:20:17.91,Default,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,如果遇上了活着的狼獾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.68,0:20:21.35,annotation,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,静留的父亲在7G后\N和消防队的伙伴们一起\N踏上了探索这个世界的旅程\N已经过去了近两年，但仍然音讯全无\N他曾说过两周后就会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.12,0:20:21.44,Default,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,记得叫他别鬼混了 快点回家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.56,0:20:22.40,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.62,0:20:24.16,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我会如实传达给父亲的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.39,0:20:25.49,Default,Iguchi,0,0,0,,星抚子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.39,0:20:25.49,annotation,Iguchi,0,0,0,,抚子是高三学生\N静留和叶香是高二学生\N玲实是高一学生\N晶是初三学生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.71,0:20:26.18,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.18,0:20:27.17,Default,Iguchi,0,0,0,,久贺玲实
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.33,0:20:27.80,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.99,0:20:29.25,Default,Iguchi,0,0,0,,东云晶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.40,0:20:29.88,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.01,0:20:32.45,Default,Iguchi,0,0,0,,中富叶香 请假
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.57,0:20:33.76,Default,Iguchi,0,0,0,,千仓静留
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.05,0:20:36.19,Default,Iguchi,0,0,0,,静留她又逃课了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.28,0:20:38.68,Default,Iguchi,0,0,0,,你们三个知道她干什么去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.80,0:20:42.89,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,前天傍晚遇到的时候 她说自己解开了帽子之谜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.01,0:20:45.77,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,在车站前和波奇一起跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.77,0:20:46.70,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,什么之谜？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.80,0:20:48.76,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,不是 她逃课是要干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.88,0:20:49.51,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,不良？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.61,0:20:51.22,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留变成不良少女了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.22,0:20:53.94,Default,Iguchi,0,0,0,,本地可没有养成不良行为的土壤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.05,0:20:56.14,Default,Iguchi,0,0,0,,这点我倒觉得不必担心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.43,0:21:00.74,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,井口老师 承蒙您的关照
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.91,0:21:02.02,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我要退学了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.07,0:21:02.90,Default,Group,0,0,0,,诶？！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.02,0:21:05.38,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,正常 正常 正常
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.54,0:21:07.52,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,正常 正常 正常 正常
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.57,0:21:08.25,Zenjiro,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.34,0:21:11.41,Zenjiro,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,虽然我没法和你同行 但你总会有办法的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.65,0:21:14.65,Zenjiro,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,用你的眼睛见证这被7G所崩坏的世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.84,0:21:16.47,Zenjiro,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,我期待着你的报告
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.52,0:21:19.06,Zenjiro,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,听好了 最重要的是保证自己的生存…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.86,0:21:22.66,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊 又是说到一半就
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.88,0:21:23.95,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嘛 但是 无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.95,0:21:24.88,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我大概清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.07,0:21:25.63,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,一点也不好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.63,0:21:26.42,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.81,0:21:26.58,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,{\an8}根本不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.58,0:21:27.59,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶 吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.74,0:21:29.94,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,你才是吓我们一大跳的吧 静留
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.05,0:21:31.51,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,你说要退学 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.57,0:21:32.25,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.25,0:21:33.41,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,之后就拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.41,0:21:34.34,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我现在就出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.34,0:21:35.23,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,诶 去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.31,0:21:37.30,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.33,0:21:39.54,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶？真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.54,0:21:40.82,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,怎么这么突然就
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.84,0:21:42.14,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这可不突然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.14,0:21:43.50,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我可是好好准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.56,0:21:48.92,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,呜哇 动起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.52,0:21:50.73,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,等会 我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.86,0:21:51.86,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.86,0:21:52.57,Default,Group,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.57,0:21:53.24,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,等会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.33,0:21:55.43,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,真的 别 不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.34,0:02:53.32,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,Ga-tan go-ton ga-tan go-ton
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.32,0:02:56.71,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,Shoo shoo train 終 終 トレイン
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.71,0:02:58.56,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,Ga-tan go-ton ga-tan go-ton
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.56,0:03:01.46,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,しょっちゅう 停止 停止
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.09,0:03:05.92,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,仲良くゆこう 電車乗って
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.36,0:03:11.19,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,大好きなもの リュックに詰めて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.63,0:03:17.92,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,ほらここが始発駅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.03,0:03:25.46,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,ラララ 知らない場所へ導いて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.46,0:03:31.42,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,キミを探す旅へ出るのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.42,0:03:33.38,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,Ga-tan go-ton ga-tan go-ton
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.06,0:03:36.16,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,ワクワクスル
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.66,0:03:38.69,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,Ga-tan go-ton ga-tan go-ton
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:42.26,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,響け ホイッスル
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.26,0:03:47.36,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,世界が脱線しちゃっても大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.72,0:03:52.22,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,ワタシたちは進んでく どこまでも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.02,0:04:00.79,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,次はどんな扉を開けようか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.79,0:04:06.10,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,さあ 終わんない旅へ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.10,0:04:11.14,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,Ga-tan go-ton ga-tan go-ton
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.34,0:02:53.32,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,哐当 咕咚 哐当 咕咚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.32,0:02:56.71,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,咻 咻 train 终 终 列车
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.71,0:02:58.56,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,哐当 咕咚 哐当 咕咚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.56,0:03:01.46,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,总是 停止 停止
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.09,0:03:05.92,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,我们亲密地乘上电车出发
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.36,0:03:11.19,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,将喜爱的东西装进背包
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.63,0:03:17.92,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,来吧 这里就是 始发站
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.03,0:03:25.46,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,啦啦啦 列车带着我们驶向未知的场所
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.46,0:03:31.42,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,开启寻找你的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.42,0:03:33.38,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,哐当 咕咚 哐当 咕咚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.06,0:03:36.16,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,心动不已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.66,0:03:38.69,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,哐当 咕咚 哐当 咕咚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:42.26,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,鸣响吧 汽笛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.26,0:03:47.36,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,即使世界脱轨也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.72,0:03:52.22,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,我们会继续向前 不管去往何方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.02,0:04:00.79,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,列车的门扉再次打开时 那又会是怎样的世界呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.79,0:04:06.10,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,走吧 踏上永不完结的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.10,0:04:11.14,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,哐当 咕咚 哐当 咕咚
